column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq (up_ra, up_dec, up_sep) as objId FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq (up_ra, up_dec, up_sep) IS NOT # SELECT TOP # p.ra, p.dec, p.dered_g, p.dered_i, p.dered_r, p.dered_u, p.dered_z, p.obj, p.objID, p.psfMag_g, p.psfMag_i, p.psfMag_r, p.psfMag_u, p.psfMag_z, p.psfMagErr_g, p.psfMagErr_i, p.psfMagErr_r, p.psfMagErr_u, p.psfMagErr_z, p.TAI_g, IS# (s.fiberID, #) as fiberID, IS# (s.mjd, #) as mjd, IS# (s.plate, #) as plate, IS# (s.plateID, #) as plateID, IS# (s.specObjID, #) as specObjID FROM ..PhotoObj AS p LEFT OUTER JOIN ..SpecObj s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID JOIN #x AS x ON x.objID = p.objID JOIN #upload AS u ON u.up_id = x.up_id WHERE (p.type = # OR p.type = #) ORDER BY x.up_id
